SQL_STMT_U.val:
Select CLMS_ADMNO, CLMS_CLNTNO, CLNT110_NAME1, CLNT205_EMP_CONTACT, CODE_DESCRIPTION, CLMS_SIGNALTEXT, CLMS_YEAR, CLMS_MONTH from :1/CLMS
join :1/CLNT on CLNT101_ADMNO = CLMS_ADMNO and CLNT102_CLNTNO = CLMS_CLNTNO
left outer join :1/CODE on CODE_TYPE=58 and CODE_NUMBERN = CLMS_SIGNALTYPE and CODE_LANGUAGE = ':5'
where CLMS_YEAR = :2 and CLMS_MONTH = :3 and CLNT205_EMP_CONTACT = ':4'
order by CLMS_ADMNO, CLMS_CLNTNO, CLMS_SIGNALTYPE

Select CLMS_ADMNO, CLMS_CLNTNO, CLNT110_NAME1, CLNT205_EMP_CONTACT, CODE_DESCRIPTION, CLMS_SIGNALTEXT, CLMS_YEAR, CLMS_MONTH from :1/CLMS
join :1/CLNT on CLNT101_ADMNO = CLMS_ADMNO and CLNT102_CLNTNO = CLMS_CLNTNO
left outer join :1/CODE on CODE_TYPE=58 and CODE_NUMBERN = CLMS_SIGNALTYPE and CODE_LANGUAGE = ':5'
where CLMS_YEAR = :2 and CLMS_MONTH = :3 and CLNT204_EMP_COMM = ':4'
order by CLMS_ADMNO, CLMS_CLNTNO, CLMS_SIGNALTYPE

Select CLMS_ADMNO, CLMS_CLNTNO, CLNT110_NAME1, CLNT205_EMP_CONTACT, CODE_DESCRIPTION, CLMS_SIGNALTEXT, CLMS_YEAR, CLMS_MONTH from :1/CLMS
join :1/CLNT on CLNT101_ADMNO = CLMS_ADMNO and CLNT102_CLNTNO = CLMS_CLNTNO
left outer join :1/CODE on CODE_TYPE=58 and CODE_NUMBERN = CLMS_SIGNALTYPE and CODE_LANGUAGE = ':5'
join :1/HUSR on HUSR_CURRENTEMPLOYEE = 'Y' and HUSR_HUSR_ID_MNGR = ':4'
where CLMS_YEAR = :2 and CLMS_MONTH = :3 and CLNT205_EMP_CONTACT = HUSR_ID
order by CLMS_ADMNO, CLMS_CLNTNO, CLMS_SIGNALTYPE
